title: Secrets of the Winter Killer
description: Jason and Nadia just got married and are going on their honeymoon to a secluded cottage, miles away from civilization. They are enjoying each other until they learn that this town has some dark, deadly secrets. As they try to uncover them, it costs them the lives of those closest to them. Deceit and betrayal makes what they're about to find out even more terrifying than what they thought they already knew.
author: Moniqua Sexton
